title: Original Bekowa full length roof rack

posts.content:
Original Bekowa full length roof rack

Powder coated to original colour, mint condition

Inc 8 clamps, two are stamped Bekowa, 6 are not stamped but believe to be original with the plastic bolts.

I’ve looked on Samba and seen other original racks with the same clamps, one of the clamps is missing the plastic wing nut and as been replaced with a metal one

Located in Barnsley, South Yorkshire

Price £1400
